OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781743669
OL,3,CTrain crash could have been avoided if
OL,4,Cdriver had used emergency system `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FA fatal train crash could have been
OL,8,Favoided if a driver had used an
OL,9,Femergency system designed to reduce
OL,10,Fspeed, an investigation has found.
OL,12,FThey stated it had "not occurred to
OL,13,Fthem" to use their train's manually
OL,14,Foperated sander, according to a report
OL,15,Finto a head-on collision between two
OL,16,Ftrains in mid Wales on October 21 2024.
OL,18,FPassenger David Tudor Evans, 66, died
OL,19,F"as a consequence of the collision",
OL,20,Fthe Rail Accident Investigation Branch
OL,21,F(RAIB) said.
OL,26,@tD@TOUuD@EO]{D@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
